body:
You'll need to run configure first before building TF desktop binaries.

On Apr 21, 2017 12:08 AM, "anonym24" <notifications@github.com> wrote:

> @andrewharp <https://github.com/andrewharp>
>
> I'd suggest trying to quantize the graph to bring the size down as much as
> possible as a first step.
>
> I get an error:
>
> ~/Desktop/tensorflow-master$ bazel build tensorflow/tools/graph_transforms:transform_graph
> ERROR: /home/osboxes/Desktop/tensorflow-master/tensorflow/core/BUILD:1357:1: no such target '//tensorflow/tools/git:gen/spec.json': target 'gen/spec.json' not declared in package 'tensorflow/tools/git' defined by /home/osboxes/Desktop/tensorflow-master/tensorflow/tools/git/BUILD and referenced by '//tensorflow/core:version_info_gen'.
> ERROR: /home/osboxes/Desktop/tensorflow-master/tensorflow/core/BUILD:1357:1: no such target '//tensorflow/tools/git:gen/head': target 'gen/head' not declared in package 'tensorflow/tools/git' defined by /home/osboxes/Desktop/tensorflow-master/tensorflow/tools/git/BUILD and referenced by '//tensorflow/core:version_info_gen'.
> ERROR: /home/osboxes/Desktop/tensorflow-master/tensorflow/core/BUILD:1357:1: no such target '//tensorflow/tools/git:gen/branch_ref': target 'gen/branch_ref' not declared in package 'tensorflow/tools/git' defined by /home/osboxes/Desktop/tensorflow-master/tensorflow/tools/git/BUILD and referenced by '//tensorflow/core:version_info_gen'.
> ERROR: Analysis of target '//tensorflow/tools/graph_transforms:transform_graph' failed; build aborted.
